籤詩版本二:
Ke hele nei i loko a i waho o kahi hoʻomoana e ʻimi i ka pōmaikaʻi nui, e like me ka jade kīnā ʻole i huna ʻia i loko o ka pōhaku
Inā he kanaka hanohano kou e alakaʻi iā ʻoe, e hoʻopōmaikaʻi ʻia ʻoe i nā waiwai a me nā hiʻohiʻona nani i kēia manawa.
詩意:
Hōʻike kēia pōhaku hexagram i ka waiwai huna i loko.
Holo maikaʻi nā mea a pau.
解曰: E like me ka pōhaku huna jade. ʻO nā ʻōlelo aʻo a ke kanaka hanohano wale nō. Hauʻoli a haʻaheo.
籤詩故事一:
◇ Nānā ʻo Emperor Yang iā Qionghua
Hoʻomaka ka viburnum i hoʻokahi manawa i ka makahiki, a i ke ahiahi. Ua lohe ʻo Emperor Yang o ka moʻokūʻauhau Sui i kekahi e ʻōlelo ana he mea like ʻole ka pua Qionghua ma Yangzhou i ka honua, keʻokeʻo e like me ka jade, nani, palupalu a nani. Lawe lākou i ka haiā wahine imperial ma luna o ka waʻa deragona, hele lākou i Yangzhou e leʻaleʻa i nā pua, i piha i ka hanohano a me ka hoʻohiwahiwa, me nā hae e lele ana.
(ʻO ka manaʻo hoʻohālikelike o kēia moʻolelo, ʻo ia ka waiwai o nā mea e like me kēia "Qionghua.
聖意: Pomaikai ka hale, pomaikai ia iho, pomaikai ka hana, pomaikai ka mare, hanau ke kane ma Liujia, nee ka hele wawae, nee ka enuhe silika, nana ka enuhe kilika i na holoholona eono, hahai ka hooponopono. , ua lanakila ka hoʻopiʻi, maikaʻi ka waiwai nalowale, ʻo Anshan ka maʻi, aloha ka lua kupapaʻu.
古人: Nānā ʻo Emperor Yang iā Qionghua
